hudson.tasks.Shell.command:
#!c:\cygwin\bin\bash --login -i
echo $NODE_NAME
cd C:/IpPhoneAutomation/ATA && tclsh AtaExec.tcl -stop all echo Finish stop all net use
echo Check if free or busy if curl -s http://localhost/index.php/status/show.xml | grep -q status.busy./status; then echo It is busy... exit exit 1 fi
User=$artifactory_user:$artifactory_pass echo Find the Last TAG if None - $LASTBL ARTIFACTORY=https://artifactory/api/storage/ipp-release/com/ac/ipp/SFB/$BuildRelease
if [ "$LASTBL" == "None" ]; then echo curl -ks -X GET $ARTIFACTORY \| grep uri \| cut -d'"' -f4 \| grep -v https \| cut -c 2- \| sort -Vr \| head -1 LASTBL=`curl -ks -u $User -X GET $ARTIFACTORY | grep uri | cut -d'"' -f4 | grep -v https | cut -c 2- | sort -Vr | head -1` fi echo Find: $LASTBL
if [ "$LASTBL" == "" ]; then echo Not find LASTBL - Exit with error exit 1 fi echo LASTBL=${LASTBL} > ${WORKSPACE}/Sanity.prop

com.chikli.hudson.plugin.naginator.Nagin.regexpForRerun: .*(ClosedChannelno workspace from node|Workspace is not accessible).*
